# Welcome

- Press Ctrl/Cmd+K for global search (All/Group/Note)
- Use the right mini-hub for LLM search (This Note / Groups / All)
- Settings: models and performance (chunk size/overlap, debounce)

Tips:

- Drag tabs to reorder; Ctrl/Cmd-select then right-click to Merge
- Drag notes onto groups to add them; a note can be in multiple groups
- Autosave every ~500ms; snapshots enable crash recovery
